{"serial": "77021", "department_serial": 63, "code": "HK3037", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Social Survey and Statistics", "ch": "社會調查與統計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Tang,Yen-Chen"], "ch": ["湯晏甄"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "HK", "room": "216"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "客家語文暨社會科學學系", "en": "Department of Hakka Language and Social Sciences"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 7, "selected": 48, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程的目標是讓同學對民意調查的研究方法有初步的了解，課程的內容涵蓋理論與實務。在民調方面，會介紹民意的形成與特質、蒐集民意的各種調查研究方式、調查研究方法的邏輯，以及問卷設計。在統計方面，藉由了解量化研究的基本概念，以及實際電腦統計軟體操作，引導同學使用統計方法探究社會科學關心的各種重要議題，客觀分析政治、社會以及經濟等現象。", "en": "The objective of this course is to provide students with a basic understanding of research methods in public opinion surveys. The course content covers both theory and practice. Regarding opinion polling, it will introduce the formation and characteristics of public opinion, various survey research methods for collecting public opinion, the logic of survey research methods, and questionnaire design. In terms of statistics, students will learn the basic concepts of quantitative research and gain practical experience in using statistical software. This will enable them to explore important issues in social sciences and objectively analyze political, social, and economic phenomena."}, "outline": {"ch": "Week 1 (9/11):課程介紹\nWeek 2 (9/18):調查的基礎：社會科學研究邏輯及理論建構\nWeek 3 (9/25):調查的工具：概念操作化與測量\nWeek 4 (10/2):選擇合適的資料蒐集方法、資料庫說明、調查的類型與抽樣\nWeek 5 (10/9):網路問卷構思設計\nWeek 6 (10/16): 調查的分析:初等統計與統計軟體操作(一)\nWeek 7 (10/23): 調查的分析:初等統計與統計軟體操作(二)\nWeek 8 (10/30):期中分組報告\nWeek 9 (11/6): 調查的分析:初等統計與統計軟體操作(三)\nWeek 10 (11/13):調查的分析:相關分析與統計軟體操作\nWeek 11 (11/20):全校運動會放假\nWeek 12 (11/27):調查的分析:獨立樣本t檢定與統計軟體操作\nWeek 13 (12/4):調查的分析:變異數分析與統計軟體操作\nWeek 14 (12/11):調查的分析:卡方檢定與統計軟體操作\nWeek 15 (12/18):專家演講(暫定)\nWeek 16 (12/25):期末分組報告\nWeek 17 (1/1):教師彈性教學週\nWeek 18 (1/8):教師彈性教學週\n*詳細清單請見開學第一週課堂發放的授課大綱", "en": "Week 1 (9/11):Course introduction\nWeek 2 (9/18):The basis of investigation: the logic of social science research and theoretical construction\nWeek 3 (9/25):Tools for investigation: conceptualization and measurement\nWeek 4 (10/2):Selection of appropriate data collection methods, database specifications, types of surveys and sampling\nWeek 5 (10/9):Internet questionnaire conception and design\nWeek 6 (10/16):Survey Analysis: Elementary Statistics and SPSS Software Operation (1)\nWeek 7 (10/23):Survey Analysis: Elementary Statistics and SPSS Software Operation (2)\nWeek 8 (10/30):Mid-term group presentation\nWeek 9 (11/6):Survey Analysis: Elementary Statistics and SPSS Software Operation (3)\nWeek 10 (11/13):Related analysis and statistical software operation\nWeek 11 (11/20):The whole school will have a holiday for the sports day\nWeek 12 (11/27):Independent sample t test and statistical software operation\nWeek 13 (12/4):ANOVA and statistical software operation\nWeek 14 (12/11):Chi-square verification and statistical software operation\nWeek 15 (12/18):Expert speech(tentative)\nWeek 16 (12/25):Final Report by group\nWeek 17 (1/1):Teacher Resilience Week\nWeek 18 (1/8):Teacher Resilience Week\n*For a detailed list, please refer to the course syllabus distributed during the first week of classes."}, "textbook": {"ch": "一、教科書:\n1.羅清俊，2016，《社會科學研究方法：打開天窗說量化》（三版），臺北：揚智出版社。\n2.顏志龍、鄭中平，2019，《給論文寫作者的統計指南：傻瓜也會跑統計》（三版）。臺北：五南。\n二、參考書:\n1.陳陸輝主編，2020，《民意調查》，台北：五南出版社。\n2.林惠玲、陳正倉，2020，《現代統計學》（第二版），台北:雙葉書廊。\n三、教師自編教材", "en": "一、Textbook:\n1.Luo Qingjun, 2016, “Social Science Research Method: Open the Skylight and Talk about Quantification“ (third edition), Taipei: Yangzhi Publishing House.\n2. Yan Zhilong and Zheng Zhongping (2019). “A Statistical Guide for Authors of Papers: Stupid Can Run Statistics“ (third edition). Taipei: Wunan.\n二、Reference books:\n1. Edited by Chen Luhui, 2020, “Public Opinion Survey“, Taipei: Wunan Publishing House.\n2. Lin Huiling and Chen Zhengcang, 2020, “Modern Statistics“ (Second Edition), Taipei: Shuangye Bookstore.\n三、Teaching materials compiled by teachers"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "80", "en": "80"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1.課堂發言討論與課堂實作:40％\n2.分組期中報告:30％\n3.分組期末報告:30％", "en": "1. Participation in classroom presentation and  practice: 40％.\n2. Midterm group report: 30％.\n3. Final group report: 30％."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期四11:00~12:00 (請先預約)", "en": "Thursday(11:00~12:00)(Please make an appointment in advance)"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "準備期末分組報告", "en": "Prepare final group report"}, "domain": {"ch": "社會思潮領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n法政領域", "en": "社會思潮領域\n\n\n、\n\n\n法政領域"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "具備客家語言文化的基本能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備社會科學的學科能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備人文關懷的精神", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "具備掌握時勢脈動與創新發展的視野", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "The basic ability of Hakka language and culture", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "The academic ability of social sciences", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "The spirit of humanity", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments"